name: Makinami Mari Illustrious (Evangelion)
description:
Lora model for Makinami Mari Illustrious from Rebuild of Evangelion movies. I made all the preview images with weight 0.8.

I've cut corners slightly because I initially planned to train the model on her green, pink and white plugsuits and the school uniform, but when browsing the images I found out she actually had two pink plugsuits. I sticked to my plan through and ignored one, sorry for that ^_^;

Prompts for each outfit:

School uniform - makinami mari illustrious, hairband, red-framed eyewear, school uniform, plaid skirt, thighhighs, necktie, shoes

Pink plugsuit - makinami mari illustrious, pink bodysuit, hairband, red-framed eyewear

Green plugsuit - makinami mari illustrious, green bodysuit, hairband, red-framed eyewear

White plugsuit - makinami mari illustrious, hairband, red-framed eyewear, white bodysuit
